Package com.example.fitnesstracker

Class ObjectLift

java.lang.Object
com.example.fitnesstracker.ObjectLift
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ObjectLift extends Object implements Serializable
Class representing a lift exercise in the fitness tracker. It contains details such as title, description, type, muscle group, equipment, and level.
Author:
Miles Nichols
